question: Question: The oldest lighthouse in this state is the Portland Head Light, while the most amusingly-named one is either Ladies Delight Light or The Cuckolds Light.  [10] Identify this state, in which Mount Katahdin serves as the northern terminus of the Appalachian Trail. It's the northeasternmost state in the continental U.S.
